title: Underrated Entities with Omar Ruiz
itunes:title: Underrated Entities with Omar Ruiz
description:
A room filled with heroes - Gregg Rosenthal, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling are joined by NFL Network's Omar Ruiz to discuss all things news including the Titans trying to resigning Ryan Tannehill (06:20) and Marshal Yanda retiring. (13:47) The heroes put Omar on the hot seat (30:36) before talking about underrated entities entering free agency. (38:42)
